<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THLACAMMI VIALTE CH410</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lunglawmhnak thawngtha bia kha, Khua zakip ah thanh u, An thahmi Jesuh
 thawng in, Khamhnak thachin bia kha, A zungzal thawngthabia kha, A
 bia-kamnak a si; Bawi Jesuh a zummi nih, Laksawng tha an hmuh lai.

[C1]
   Bawipa, Pathian sinah thlacammi vialte nih Pathian khamhnak kha a
   ngai te an hmuh te lai, Bawipa Pathian sinah thlacammi vialte nih Pathian
   khamhnak kha a ngai te an hmuh te lai.

[V2]
 Khuamui chungah a um i, Sualnak lam a zulmi, Pathian dawtnak kha zoh
 u, Bawi Jesuh kha zum u, Lungthin nan ngeihmi vial in, A bia-kamnak zum
 u, Bawipa sin thlacammi nih, Rawhnak an phan lai lo.

[C2]
   Bawipa, Pathian sinah thlacammi vialte nih Pathian khamhnak kha a
   ngai te an hmuh te lai, Bawipa Pathian sinah thlacammi vialte nih Pathian
   khamhnak kha a ngai te an hmuh te lai.

[V3]
 Vaw leicung phorh ritmi le, Sifah a ingmi hna, Nan thilrit kha chan
 awkah, Jesuh nih an ngan hna, A sungbik nunnak laksawng, Mi vialte a pek
 hna, Zumhnak in a halmi cu khi laksawng an hmu lai.

[C3]
   Bawipa, Pathian sinah thlacammi vialte nih Pathian khamhnak kha a
   ngai te an hmuh te lai, Bawipa Pathian sinah thlacammi vialte nih Pathian
   khamhnak kha a ngai te an hmuh te lai.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<hymn_number>410</hymn_number>
</song>